params.text: # Past tumor volume embedding with LSTM

# Extracting the graph embedding

We mean-pool the node embeddings of each node type, then concatenate these vectors.

# Knowledge graph embedding with GNN

This heterogeneous graph convolution creates node embeddings for all genes, diseases, and drugs in the graph.

# Tumor volume trajectory predictions with ODE

An MLP is used to predict the derivative of the tumor volume at different stages, based on the knowledge graph embedding and the past tumor volume embeddings.

# Training configuration

The loss for the whole model is simply the MSE loss over the future volume measurements.
